<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" package="com.example.picasso">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="14" android:targetSdkVersion="P" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_CONTACTS" />
	<application android:theme="resourceId:0x7f0a0005" android:label="Picasso Samples" android:icon="res/drawable-mdpi-v4/icon.png" android:testOnly="true" android:allowBackup="false" android:supportsRtl="false">
		<activity android:label="Picasso Samples" android:name="com.example.picasso.SampleGridViewActivity">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<activity android:name="com.example.picasso.SampleContactsActivity" />
		<activity android:name="com.example.picasso.SampleGalleryActivity" />
		<activity android:name="com.example.picasso.SampleListDetailActivity" />
		<receiver android:name="com.example.picasso.SampleWidgetProvider">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.appwidget.action.APPWIDGET_UPDATE" />
			</intent-filter>
			<meta-data android:name="android.appwidget.provider" android:resource="res/xml/sample_widget_info.xml" />
		</receiver>
		<provider android:name="com.squareup.picasso3.provider.PicassoContentProvider" android:exported="false" android:authorities="com.example.picasso.com.squareup.picasso3" />
	</application>
</manifest>
